Query Plan
===================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                             |NAME    |
---------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT            |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                 |:EX10001|
|2 |  └─SORT                             |        |
|3 |    └─WINDOW FUNCTION                |        |
|4 |      └─PARTITION SORT               |        |
|5 |        └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|6 |          └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)|:EX10000|
|7 |            └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |
|8 |              └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |test1   |
===================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(test1.c2, T_FUN_MAX(test1.c1))]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      sort_keys([test1.c1, ASC])
  1 - output([test1.c1], [INTERNAL_FUNCTION(test1.c2, T_FUN_MAX(test1.c1))]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      dop=3
  2 - output([test1.c1], [T_FUN_MAX(test1.c1)], [test1.c2]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      sort_keys([test1.c1, ASC])
  3 - output([test1.c1], [T_FUN_MAX(test1.c1)], [test1.c2]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      win_expr(T_FUN_MAX(test1.c1)), partition_by([test1.c3]), order_by(nil), window_type(RANGE), upper(UNBOUNDED PRECEDING), lower(UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING)
  4 - output([test1.c1], [test1.c3], [test1.c2]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      sort_keys([HASH(test1.c3), ASC], [test1.c3, ASC])
  5 - output([test1.c1], [test1.c3], [test1.c2]), filter(nil), rowset=256
